#, no-c-format
msgid "This manual page was written by &Burkhard.Lueck; &Burkhard.Lueck.mail;."
msgstr "यह मैनुअल पेज &Burkhard.Lueck द्वारा लिखा गया था; &बर्कहार्ड.लुएक.मेल;."
